  <div class="call-banner"><div class="wrap"><span>Traeger pellet grill service?</span><a href="tel:+14243250520" class="phone-lg">(424) 325-0520</a></div></div>

  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap"><div class="hero-grid"><div class="hero-text">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › Traeger › Grill Repair</div>
    <h1>Traeger Pellet Grill Repair</h1>
    <p class="lede">Traeger pellet grills are a <b>fundamentally different appliance architecture from gas grills</b> — compressed wood pellets fed by an auger into a firepot, induction fan forcing airflow, hot-rod ceramic igniter lighting the initial pellet load, PID controller managing target temperature via RTD feedback. No burners, no gas valves, no flame carrier — the failure modes are completely different from Weber, Napoleon, Coyote, or luxury built-in gas grills. We service the full Traeger US residential lineup: <b>Pro series</b> entry (Pro 575/780 barrel-style), <b>Ironwood</b> mid-premium (double-wall insulation + Super Smoke), <b>Timberline</b> flagship (Timberline XL with induction burners on the newer generation). WiFIRE app pairing across all current-gen units. Technicians unfamiliar with pellet architecture often mis-diagnose Traeger failures — our team trains specifically on pellet-grill diagnostic protocol. Same-day dispatch, $89 residential diagnostic waived with the repair.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta"><a href="tel:+14243250520" class="btn btn-primary">Call (424) 325-0520</a><a href="#book" class="btn btn-ghost">Request a Visit</a></div>
    <ul class="hero-facts">
      <li><b>Pellet architecture ≠ gas grill</b> — auger + induction fan + hot-rod igniter + PID</li>
      <li><b>Pro + Ironwood + Timberline</b> — three-tier US residential lineup</li>
      <li><b>WiFIRE WiFi pairing</b> + Super Smoke mode + Pop-and-Lock storage</li>
      <li><b>$89 residential diagnostic</b> — waived when you authorize the repair</li>
    </ul>
  </div><aside class="hero-aside"><div class="aside-card"><h3>Talk to a local branch</h3>
    <a href="tel:+13238704790" class="branch"><b>West Hollywood</b><span>(323) 870-4790</span></a>
