    <h2>What Traeger pellet grill repair costs in LA</h2>
    <table class="price-table">
      <tr><th>Service</th><th>Typical Range</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Residential diagnostic</td><td>$89</td><td>Waived with repair</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Pellet jam clearing + moisture check</td><td>$89 diag only</td><td>Resolves ~50% of auger calls</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Auger motor</td><td>$180 – $280</td><td>Pellet-feed mechanism</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Auger shear pin</td><td>$30 – $60</td><td>Sacrificial motor protection</td></tr>
